    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 requirements for MRL 2 Class II device. Validation results demonstrate CFD model predicts relative hemolysis index within ±12% of experimental benchmark across all operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The validation configuration (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7-rc2) is considered representative of the current production solver (ansys-cfx-15-build-2026-q1-build-7) based on change-log review confirming no solver physics changes between rc2 and final release. Credibility evidence is assessed as sufficient to support the COU decision.",
